description.en: A personal mailbox, ie. an Internet mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the first owner of this mailbox. This is a 'static inverse functional property', in that  there is (across time and change) at most one individual that ever has any particular value for foaf:mbox.

label.en: sha1sum of a personal mailbox URI name

description.en: The sha1sum of the URI of an Internet mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the  first owner of the mailbox.
